nodes.text: This seminar was to happen with the confirmed participation of mOKDAR 15, Skreen, Kaat Thrick-Thrick, Aanxi Raanxi Laanxi and 26-424, although 26-424 refused to take part but had presence confirmed for the feedings.

This unnamed seminar was mentioned in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
